1.npm init -y
    for this command package.json file will be create.

2.npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer vite 
    same as documention but we only add vite it will work like a live server no need to relode.
    this code will create:
    i) node modules folder
    ii) package-lock.json
 
3. npx tailwindcss init -p 
    same as documention but we only add -p because use use postcss as a same time
    this code will create:
    i) postcss.config.js
    ii) tailwind.config.js

4) in tailwind.config.js file change like this 
     content: ['*'],

5) in package.json 
     "start": "echo \"Error: no test specified\" && exit 1" ---- replace) with this code
    "start": "vite"

6)  @tailwind base;
    @tailwind components;
    @tailwind utilities;

    paste this 3 code in own css file..
    we use css/tailwind.css so we paste this code in tailwind.css file

7) npm run start